  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of ASF-1096 Cream 0.5% in the Treatment of Patients With Newly Developed Discoid Lupus Erythematosus (DLE) Lesions. An International Multi-Centre Clinical Phase 2, Placebo Controlled and Double Blind Proof of Concept Study (2)</official_title>
